---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Liteworks Co." description="Privacy Policy for Liteworks Co., Greater Cincinnati's trusted excavation and sitework experts.">
  <Header client:load />
  
  <main class="bg-white pt-28 pb-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-10">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none space-y-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">1. Who We Are</h2>
          <p>
            Liteworks Co. ("we," "us," or "our") operates this website. We are a site preparation and excavation company located at:
          </p>
          <address class="not-italic mt-3 pl-4 border-l-2 border-[#c4d931]">
            1481 SR 28, Suite 901<br />
            Loveland, OH 45140<br />
            <a href="mailto:team@liteworksco.com" class="text-[#c4d931] hover:underline">team@liteworksco.com</a>
          </address>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">2. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>When you submit a quote request or contact form on our website, we collect:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-3 space-y-1">
            <li>Full name</li>
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>Phone number</li>
            <li>Project details you provide in the message field</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">We also collect standard website analytics data (pages visited, browser type, referring site) through our hosting provider. This data is not personally identifiable.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>We use the information you provide to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-3 space-y-1">
            <li>Respond to your quote request or inquiry</li>
            <li>Schedule site visits or consultations</li>
            <li>Send project-related communications</li>
            <li>Improve our website and services</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">4. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>
            We retain your contact information for as long as necessary to fulfill your service request and for reasonable follow-up. If you would like your information removed from our records, contact us at <a href="mailto:team@liteworksco.com" class="text-[#c4d931] hover:underline">team@liteworksco.com</a> and we will delete it promptly.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">5. Cookies</h2>
          <p>
            Our website may use basic cookies to improve site functionality. We do not use tracking cookies for advertising purposes. You can disable cookies in your browser settings at any time.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">6. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>
            Our website may be hosted on or use services provided by third parties (such as hosting providers or form processors). These services have their own privacy policies. We select providers who handle data responsibly.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">7. Security</h2>
          <p>
            We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access or disclosure. However, no internet transmission is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">8. Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            Our website is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-3">10. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            Questions about this policy? Reach out at <a href="mailto:team@liteworksco.com" class="text-[#c4d931] hover:underline">team@liteworksco.com</a> or call <a href="tel:5139279675" class="text-[#c4d931] hover:underline">(513) 927-9675</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
